race.comment: Sticking with the honest STEWART (8) who is long overdue and bursting to win. Just missed here two back before a close-up sixth last time. Well placed this line-up and won't get a better chance to break through. FINANCE SHOGUN (1) is fitter for three runs back and put the writing on the wall here last time with a solid third. Was about a length behind STEWART. Ready now after three runs back and gets chance. EPICUS (2) has been freshened since last time when well off best but well worth another chance. ARROANCE (11) is coming off picnic form and with the huge weight drop can sneak into the finish.
